{"version":3,"kind":"Notebook","sha256":"36042ee17c44fc5fb9ed247f192bde4012cc7b93fd628768c9f1fcec85710d60","slug":"chapter03-sec02","location":"/chapter03/chapter03_sec02.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"Wie interpretiere ich das Meshroom-Ergebnis?","kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"content_includes_title":false,"authors":[{"id":"Simone Gramsch","name":"Simone Gramsch"}],"open_access":true,"license":{"content":{"id":"CC-BY-NC-SA-4.0","url":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/","name":"Creative Commons Attribution Non Commercial Share Alike 4.0 International","CC":true}},"github":"https://github.com/gramschs/thma_virtual_engineering","numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"source_url":"https://github.com/gramschs/thma_virtual_engineering/blob/main/chapter03/chapter03_sec02.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/gramschs/thma_virtual_engineering/edit/main/chapter03/chapter03_sec02.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"chapter03_sec02.md","url":"/thma_virtual_engineering/build/chapter03_sec02-2235cb4f5413cf557cceb5ac5b9433e8.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Meshroom hat die Pipeline durchlaufen, und im 3D-Viewer erscheint das erste\nModell der Kugelbahn. Doch was genau bedeuten die grünen und roten\nKamerasymbole? Warum ist die dichte Punktwolke an manchen Stellen auffällig\ndünn, und weshalb sieht die Textur stellenweise wie ein unscharfer Fleck aus?\nDie Qualitätskriterien aus Abschnitt 3.1 liefern jetzt den Maßstab, um diese\nFragen zu beantworten.","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"nejF8xhHSo"}],"key":"zGu9OXTtXX"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lernziele","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"LHDKqvhWo9"}],"identifier":"lernziele","label":"Lernziele","html_id":"lernziele","implicit":true,"key":"GOVNwnh4hw"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lernziele","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"EGMyZAy2nh"}],"key":"DGwMMGCfdB"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie können die dünn besetzte und die dicht besetzte Punktwolke in Meshroom\nqualitativ beurteilen.","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"PoGYxYhRfA"}],"key":"gBodVsQEA1"}],"checked":false,"key":"LJJyBTY8qb"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie können anhand der Kamerapositions-Heatmap einschätzen, welche Bereiche\ndes Modells gut und welche schlecht rekonstruiert wurden.","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"g6jgSAgaxa"}],"key":"JKtKOOCPfp"}],"checked":false,"key":"MPzGDesGpR"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie können erklären, wie Textur auf ein Mesh projiziert wird, und Merkmale\nschlechter Texturierung benennen.","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"xRmjhKtMI3"}],"key":"lblNSfKBb8"}],"checked":false,"key":"edYM1VlHVa"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie können mindestens vier typische Fehlermuster in Meshroom-Ergebnissen\nbenennen und deren Ursachen erklären.","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"N5sSTpUAEO"}],"key":"btlTgTiZKz"}],"checked":false,"key":"ewejHBVcgB"}],"key":"SX7a6G76Vj"}],"class":"attention","key":"CPjxpdIMbM"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was bedeutet ein erfolgreicher Pipeline-Durchlauf?","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"fBitVMnk42"}],"identifier":"was-bedeutet-ein-erfolgreicher-pipeline-durchlauf","label":"Was bedeutet ein erfolgreicher Pipeline-Durchlauf?","html_id":"was-bedeutet-ein-erfolgreicher-pipeline-durchlauf","implicit":true,"key":"gT05EdzLJG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Meshroom zeigt uns nach einem erfolgreichen Durchlauf den grünen Haken an allen\nKnoten der Pipeline. Das bedeutet: Alle Berechnungsschritte wurden fehlerfrei\nabgeschlossen. Doch was bedeuten die Farben in der Punktwolke, warum sind manche\nKamerasymbole grün und andere gelb, und weshalb sieht die Textur auf dem Mesh\nstellenweise wie ein unscharfer Fleck aus?","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"DKNmdXqpp0"}],"key":"ajSQAYN2wA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ein fehlerfreier Algorithmus-Durchlauf ist nicht dasselbe wie ein gutes Ergebnis.","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"M9ezwMmC82"}],"key":"tGevPdTWTc"}],"key":"e8L510vNXi"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die Qualität des Meshes hängt nicht davon ab, ob Meshroom “durchgelaufen” ist,\nsondern davon, wie gut die Eingabefotos die Geometrie des Objekts abgedeckt\nhaben. In Abschnitt 3.1 haben wir gelernt, welche Qualitätskriterien ein gutes\nMesh auszeichnen. Jetzt lernen wir, wie wir diese Kriterien direkt an der\nMeshroom-Ausgabe ablesen können.","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"GA78fWl06c"}],"key":"jklJZBeU3F"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was verrät die dünn besetzte Punktwolke?","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"gvRfYOiTzb"}],"identifier":"was-verr-t-die-d-nn-besetzte-punktwolke","label":"Was verrät die dünn besetzte Punktwolke?","html_id":"was-verr-t-die-d-nn-besetzte-punktwolke","implicit":true,"key":"tclCWPD2E0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Der erste sichtbare Schritt in der Meshroom-Pipeline ist die ","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"NZtpKBL7jp"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"dünn besetzte\nPunktwolke","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"OMAAPxZlm6"}],"key":"Pu53TxXMEt"},{"type":"text","value":" (englisch: “Sparse Point Cloud”). Sie entsteht im Knoten\n“FeatureExtraction” und “StructureFromMotion” (SfM) und enthält typischerweise\neinige zehntausend Punkte, also deutlich weniger als das spätere dichte Mesh,\naber ausreichend, um die Rekonstruktionsqualität früh zu beurteilen.","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"T14olEe2DH"}],"key":"gJ9vAY8pro"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die dünn besetzte Punktwolke zeigt uns zwei Dinge gleichzeitig: die grobe\nGeometrie des Objekts und die rekonstruierten Kamerapositionen. Jede Kamera wird\nals kleines Pyramidensymbol dargestellt. Die Farbe dieser Symbole ist der erste\nwichtige Qualitätsindikator:","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"key":"Ca2JSxq78m"}],"key":"fSdQMw2Ziq"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":66,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Grüne Kameras","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"X1f7p2uCSm"}],"key":"e1Cl1w2AyX"},{"type":"text","value":": Die Kameraposition wurde mit hoher Konfidenz rekonstruiert.\nDas Foto hat viele übereinstimmende Feature-Punkte mit seinen Nachbaraufnahmen\ngeliefert.","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"qSajdRwqCn"}],"key":"j62ehDhRQm"}],"key":"V5cWCH2Iom"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":62,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":62,"column":1},"end":{"line":62,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gelbe Kameras","position":{"start":{"line":62,"column":1},"end":{"line":62,"column":1}},"key":"QiQwQoYSgM"}],"key":"hXvuoOG2dq"},{"type":"text","value":": Die Rekonstruktion war weniger sicher, meistens wegen zu\ngeringer Überlappung oder schlechter Textur in diesem Bereich.","position":{"start":{"line":62,"column":1},"end":{"line":62,"column":1}},"key":"g3VoJQs9mH"}],"key":"HSomHU7oDI"}],"key":"WCwZ9rzHGa"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":66,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Rote oder fehlende Kameras","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"key":"QRH6oy7a6s"}],"key":"HQmCDDNVlA"},{"type":"text","value":": Meshroom konnte diese Fotos nicht in die\nRekonstruktion einbinden. Sie liefern keinen Beitrag zum Mesh.","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"key":"nHnXq7GaNG"}],"key":"TinqgyZp43"}],"key":"gggBzaMaNU"}],"key":"V3UwKibdGF"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was tun wir, wenn viele Kameras rot sind?","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"key":"dLyCPU7mpu"}],"key":"gEKso7eJV8"}],"key":"X1HP0jjZHz"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Rote Kameras weisen fast immer auf einen Fehler beim Fotografieren hin: zu\nwenige überlappende Aufnahmen, zu glatte Oberflächen ohne Textur oder starke\nBeleuchtungsunterschiede zwischen den Fotos. Die Lösung liegt nicht in Meshroom,\nsondern im Aufnahmeschritt, ein wichtiger Grund, warum wir in Kapitel 2 so viel\nSorgfalt auf die Aufnahmestrategie verwendet haben.","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"column":1}},"key":"QsvYlQ9s0H"}],"key":"WUwcAcKOwc"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":78,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Neben den Kamerapositionen zeigt uns die dünn besetzte Punktwolke auch, welche\nBereiche des Objekts überhaupt rekonstruiert werden konnten. Bereiche, in denen\ndie Punktwolke auffällig leer ist, werden sehr wahrscheinlich auch im finalen\nMesh Lücken aufweisen.","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"key":"zp6VycHyYR"}],"key":"iJEr71km1Q"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mini-Übung","position":{"start":{"line":80,"column":1},"end":{"line":80,"column":1}},"key":"Fu6W1AnEfc"}],"key":"illCbIkN3R"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":84,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie öffnen ein Meshroom-Projekt und sehen in der dünn besetzten Punktwolke: Von\n80 Fotos wurden 72 als grüne Kameras rekonstruiert. Die restlichen 8 sind rot,\nallesamt Aufnahmen der Unterseite der Kugelbahn.","position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":82,"column":1}},"key":"xCPaO1sug1"}],"key":"Fr65DMWFjl"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":88,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":86,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was erwarten Sie für das finale Mesh an der Unterseite des Objekts?","position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":86,"column":1}},"key":"InAwBv0rYp"}],"key":"jHZMon6G6j"}],"key":"XZTZwyfE5K"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":87,"column":1},"end":{"line":88,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Welche Maßnahme hätte das Problem bereits beim Fotografieren verhindern\nkönnen?","position":{"start":{"line":87,"column":1},"end":{"line":87,"column":1}},"key":"nyZbkFWHd2"}],"key":"nqoWU92cgF"}],"key":"MeDJXEyenO"}],"key":"prnpqXc8D0"}],"class":"tip","key":"CuiMdHl1ow"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lösung","position":{"start":{"line":91,"column":1},"end":{"line":91,"column":1}},"key":"Es1rvCeLkk"}],"key":"pozPpOrZLE"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":94,"column":1},"end":{"line":100,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":94,"column":1},"end":{"line":97,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":94,"column":1},"end":{"line":96,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"An der Unterseite der Kugelbahn sind Lücken im Mesh zu erwarten, da Meshroom\nkeine Kamerasichten für diesen Bereich rekonstruieren konnte. Ohne Kamerapositions-\ninformation fehlen dem SfM-Algorithmus die nötigen Tiefeninformationen.","position":{"start":{"line":94,"column":1},"end":{"line":94,"column":1}},"key":"cRK8sx7fZy"}],"key":"zFZbpXoNaF"}],"key":"wHNvtsEd5r"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":98,"column":1},"end":{"line":100,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":98,"column":1},"end":{"line":100,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mehr Überlappungsaufnahmen von der Unterseite hätten das Problem verhindert.\nPraktisch: Das Objekt auf einem Drehteller oder einem Stativ positionieren,\nsodass Aufnahmen aus verschiedenen Höhenwinkeln (auch von unten) möglich sind.","position":{"start":{"line":98,"column":1},"end":{"line":98,"column":1}},"key":"sV74BbKcpn"}],"key":"AJagzKmqDq"}],"key":"f1CBdDAS5U"}],"key":"D1TtXziI7b"}],"class":"tip dropdown","key":"SWiKM9Q1Bo"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":103,"column":1},"end":{"line":103,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was verrät die dicht besetzte Punktwolke?","position":{"start":{"line":103,"column":1},"end":{"line":103,"column":1}},"key":"nG60zY5lL1"}],"identifier":"was-verr-t-die-dicht-besetzte-punktwolke","label":"Was verrät die dicht besetzte Punktwolke?","html_id":"was-verr-t-die-dicht-besetzte-punktwolke","implicit":true,"key":"gCmgdc23ku"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1},"end":{"line":107,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nach dem SfM-Schritt berechnet Meshroom die ","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1},"end":{"line":105,"column":1}},"key":"xDgzQ1b8Bd"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1},"end":{"line":105,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"dicht besetzte Punktwolke","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1},"end":{"line":105,"column":1}},"key":"hhQdMbAh6O"}],"key":"ahvHgpnfsD"},{"type":"text","value":"\n(englisch: “Dense Point Cloud”) im Knoten “DepthMap” und “Meshing”. Sie enthält\noft mehrere Millionen Punkte und liefert die Grundlage für das eigentliche Mesh.","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1},"end":{"line":105,"column":1}},"key":"ksZTlOKd2f"}],"key":"pi08qwMaMf"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":109,"column":1},"end":{"line":109,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die dichte Punktwolke beurteilen wir anhand von drei Merkmalen:","position":{"start":{"line":109,"column":1},"end":{"line":109,"column":1}},"key":"Vrgg9szXZC"}],"key":"xpnX93SN8e"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":121,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":114,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":111,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Dichte","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":111,"column":1}},"key":"pk4hScpwPp"}],"key":"J0einlGrpR"},{"type":"text","value":": Gut beleuchtete und texturreiche Bereiche erzeugen eine dichte\nPunktwolke. Glatte, einfarbige oder reflektierende Oberflächen (bei unserer\nKugelbahn zum Beispiel glänzende Metallteile) erzeugen kaum Punkte, weil der\nStereo-Matching-Algorithmus dort keine stabilen Korrespondenzen findet.","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":111,"column":1}},"key":"z7ImiuZ7Bj"}],"key":"vwayIR2EHa"}],"key":"rJbEGoVG0W"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":115,"column":1},"end":{"line":118,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":115,"column":1},"end":{"line":115,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Rauschen","position":{"start":{"line":115,"column":1},"end":{"line":115,"column":1}},"key":"nrpedkxsA5"}],"key":"ZixjM67uIV"},{"type":"text","value":": Selbst in gut rekonstruierten Bereichen streuen einzelne Punkte\nleicht um die wahre Oberfläche. Dieses Rauschen ist normal und unvermeidlich.\nProblematisch wird es, wenn ganze Bereiche weit von der tatsächlichen\nOberfläche abweichen.","position":{"start":{"line":115,"column":1},"end":{"line":115,"column":1}},"key":"yi8ybKEvh5"}],"key":"SQQpfmlQrb"}],"key":"EbXO1DyF7v"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":121,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":119,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lücken","position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":119,"column":1}},"key":"Fq6zwQ3Irw"}],"key":"X5JPl3hcB0"},{"type":"text","value":": Stellen in der dichten Punktwolke ohne Punkte werden im späteren\nMesh zu Lücken, genau wie wir es in Abschnitt 3.1 besprochen haben.","position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":119,"column":1}},"key":"vowPQXtnSF"}],"key":"wBPVJseZkV"}],"key":"iJXS0MMEcq"}],"key":"sFJ3pHp6b9"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":122,"column":1},"end":{"line":122,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wie entsteht die Textur, und woran erkenne ich eine schlechte Texturierung?","position":{"start":{"line":122,"column":1},"end":{"line":122,"column":1}},"key":"mTvK2WWWs7"}],"identifier":"wie-e